title: Sun-Ray Cinema
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Pizza, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Seatside food service in historic movie theatre features riNOTta (vegan ricotta) pizza and vegan nacho cheese. Vegan specialties are made in house (no Daiya or other processed substitutes). Also offer vegan candy including gummi bears, sour gummy worms, and locally made chocolate.
